<li id="cite_note-autogenerated2-57"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-autogenerated2_57-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Koder, S. "History of the Jews of Kerala". <i>The St. Thomas Christian Encyclopaedia of India</i>, ed. G. Menachery, 1973.</span></li>
